headline: This Week In Digital Payment - Innovation and Competition Transform Financial Services Landscape
summary: The "Beyond Banking for Consumers: The Next Frontier" report highlights a shift in the digital payment and banking sectors, driven by both financial and non-financial disruptors. It explores how global financial institutions are moving beyond traditional offerings to provide a more holistic suite of services, including financial wellness and lifestyle benefits. Key players like PayPal and Nubank are leading innovations, while Big Tech is entering the space with ambitions to create superapps...
